    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless shape\u2014it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept, so you won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
