    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered for acquisition is an exceptional specimen of precision engineering, maintained to a standard that satisfies the most exacting mechanical scrutiny. This vehicle features a high-compression, naturally aspirated power plant integrated with a close-ratio six-speed manual transaxle and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its original lateral stiffness, supported by a multi-link rear suspension and monotube dampers that exhibit zero hydraulic leakage. The braking system utilizes four-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, showing no signs of thermal stress or pad taper. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive borescope of the cylinders and a full drivetrain fluid analysis, confirming optimal internal tolerances and lubrication. Every seal, bushing, and aerodynamic undertray remains in showroom-grade state, ensuring the vehicle performs exactly as its designers intended. This is a turnkey opportunity for a collector seeking peak mechanical fidelity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
