    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather remains supple and retains its original factory aroma, with every switch and dial functioning with crisp, tactile precision. Meticulously garage-kept and maintained with an open checkbook, it comes with a complete, documented service history and all original keys. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawless example of automotive excellence that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
