      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1994 Nissan Skyline GT-R V-Spec represents a pinnacle of JDM engineering, preserved in showroom state. The RB26DETT power plant maintains factory-spec compression across all six cylinders, breathing through the original twin-turbocharged induction system with zero shaft play. The ATTESA E-TS Pro all-wheel-drive system and Super HICAS four-wheel steering operate with surgical precision, providing the mechanical grip and cornering rotation these legends are known for. Beneath the chassis, the Brembo braking system and V-Spec tuned suspension remain free of oxidation, with all bushings and ball joints showing no signs of fatigue. The paint depth is consistent throughout, and the interior retains its original textures without UV degradation. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who values mechanical integrity and period-correct authenticity.",
